name: Tungsten Bakery
description:
Meme created by @tahseensami

This piece is the tenth meme by TungstenDAO, an experimental meme incubation studio.

TungstenDAO will amass a collection of assets that are highly memeable, then create content that reinforces their social significance and strengthens memetic desires for these assets.

Drawing inspiration from NounsDAO, all holders of memes minted by TungstenDAO are members of TungstenDAO, 1 meme = 1 vote.

Governance is currently coordinated via a members only Telegram channel but we seek to have on chain governance implemented by the time 30 memes have been minted and auctioned.

The treasury is controlled exclusively via governance by holders of memes minted by TungstenDAO.
